#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilización"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The most common way to run <command>meinproc4</command> is simply as "
#| "<literallayout>\n"
#| "<userinput><command>meinproc4</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
#| "replaceable>\n"
#| "</userinput>\n"
#| "</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
#| "index.docbook. This command creates HTML pages from the DocBook file. "
#| "Note that these pages are only viewable in KDE-based browsers (like "
#| "Konqueror)."
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"O xeito máis frecuente de executar <command>meinproc4</command> é con "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc4</command> <replaceable>ficheiro-docbook</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> onde <replaceable>ficheiro-docbook</replaceable> é "
"xeralmente index.docbook. Esta orde crea páxinas HTML a partir do ficheiro "
"DocBook. Lembre que estas páxinas só se poden ver en navegadores baseados "
"ennnn KDE (como Konqueror)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you need to view the HTML output in another browser (for example, if "
#| "you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
#| "<userinput><command>meinproc4</command> --stylesheet "
#| "<replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
#| "replaceable>\n"
#| "</userinput>\n"
#| "</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
#| "full path to one of the XSL stylesheets in $KDEDIR/share/apps/ksgmltools/"
#| "customization. To produce output suitable for the web, you can use "
#| "<command>kde-web.xsl</command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</"
#| "command>. See the README file in that directory for more details."
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Se precisa ver o HTML producido en outro navegador (por exemplo, se o vai "
"pór accesíbel na internet),  use "
"<literallayout><userinput><command>meinproc4</command> --stylesheet "
"<replaceable>folla_de_estilo</replaceable> <replaceable>ficheiro-docbook</"
"replaceable></userinput></literallayout> onde <replaceable>folla_de_estilo</"
"replaceable> é a ruta completa a unha das follas de estilo XSL en $KDEDIR/"
"share/apps/ksgmltools/customization. Para obter un resultado axeitado para a "
"web, use <command>kde-web.xsl</command> ou <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</"
"command>. Consulte o ficheiro README nese directorio para máis detalles."

